Millénaire — Minecraft 26.2 (Fabric) clean-room rewrite
========================================================

LICENSE: TO BE DETERMINED (see PLAN.md §8, decision D1).

This project is a clean-room rewrite. All Java source code in src/ is written
from scratch and does not contain decompiled Minecraft code or copied code from
the original Millénaire mod.

Reused art and content data originate from the original Millénaire by Kinniken
(https://millenaire.org/, https://gitlab.com/Millenaire/Public). Their use and
any public redistribution is pending license clarification / author permission
and MUST be resolved before any public release.

Until a final license is chosen, all rights are reserved.
